JOHANNESBURG – The world premiere of “Black Panther” took place in Los Angeles and South African actors showed off their royal African themed attire on the red carpet. The much anticipated Marvel superhero blockbuster features renowned SA actors Connie Chiume and John Kani, who both attended the premier. READ: IsiXhosa will be official language in Black Panther’s Wakanda In the film Kani plays the role of King T'Chaka and Chiume plays the role of a mining tribe elder.
	The whole star-studded cast stepped out in African themed prints and style. Actors Chadwick Boseman, Angela Bassett, Lupita Nyong'o, Michael B. Jordan and Danai Gurira joined with the support of Yara Shahidi, Forest Whitaker, David Oyelowo, Janelle Monae and Issa Rae also graced the red carpet. Actor John Kani at the Los Angeles World Premiere of Marvel Studios' BLACK PANTHER at Dolby Theatre on January 29, 2018 in Hollywood, California. [Jesse Grant / GETTY IMAGES NORTH] AMERICA / AFP] Actor Janeshia Adams-Ginyard at the Los Angeles World Premiere of Marvel Studios' BLACK PANTHER at Dolby Theatre on January 29, 2018 in Hollywood, California. [Jesse Grant / GETTY IMAGES NORTH] AMERICA / AFP]  Actor Connie Chiume at the Los Angeles World Premiere of Marvel Studios' BLACK PANTHER at Dolby Theatre on January 29, 2018 in Hollywood, California. [Jesse Grant / GETTY IMAGES NORTH AMERICA / AFP] The #GQWomanOfTheDay is @Lupita_Nyongo who stars in the upcoming #BlackPanther film and looked regal at last night's premier. pic.twitter.com/cteFiaaJUM Actor John Kani on how "Black Panther" presents Africans in a new light (Watch) #BlackPantherPremiere https://t.co/jVabiJeG3f pic.twitter.com/bgCKx3PKic Yara Shahidi in Etro @ 'Black Panther' LA Premiere pic.twitter.com/oPpx15RiBk Writer/director Ryan Coogler (R) and Zinzi Evans at the Los Angeles World Premiere of Marvel Studios' BLACK PANTHER at Dolby Theatre on January 29, 2018 in Hollywood, California. [Jesse Grant / GETTY IMAGES NORTH AMERICA / AFP] Angela Bassett (@ImAngelaBassett) looking like the QUEEN she is at the premiere of #BlackPanther pic.twitter.com/KDrd2Wjp5U Actor Sydelle Noel (C) at the Los Angeles World Premiere of Marvel Studios' BLACK PANTHER at Dolby Theatre on January 29, 2018 in Hollywood, California. [Alberto E. Rodriguez / GETTY IMAGES NORTH AMERICA / AFP] Actors John Kani (L) and Atandwa Kani at the Los Angeles World Premiere of Marvel Studios' BLACK PANTHER at Dolby Theatre on January 29, 2018 in Hollyw